<br>
My aunt and uncle seem to live a pretty normal life.  They both have good jobs and like most people in the very late 70's they have taken out life insurance.  Here is where we enter the evil greed demon that takes control of the man I no longer call my uncle.  He concocts a plan to kill his wife and have it look like a murder so he can claim her insurance.  The plan is simple he and her would go for a Sunday drive, he would act like there was a flat (by taking air out of one tire) in the middle of no where.  His two co-conspirators would drive by and kill her while he &quot;went to get help&quot;.  <br>
<br>
